JOIN THE HUNT

2CP

Kroot Hunting Pack – Battle Tactic Stratagem

When a Kroot Hunting Pack closes in on its prey, there are often other hunters waiting to join in the fray and take their share of any spoils.

**WHEN:** Any phase.  
  
**TARGET:** One KROOT INFANTRY or [KROOT HOUNDS](https://wahapedia.ru/wh40k10ed/factions/t-au-empire/Kroot-Hounds) unit from your army that was just destroyed. You can use this Stratagem on that unit even though it was just destroyed.  
  
**EFFECT:** Add a new unit to your army identical to your destroyed unit, in [Strategic Reserves](https://wahapedia.ru/wh40k10ed/the-rules/core-rules/#Strategic-Reserves), at its Starting Strength.  
  
**RESTRICTIONS:** This Stratagem cannot be used to return destroyed CHARACTER units to Attached units. You can only use this Stratagem once per battle.

